                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">...you can split the gaurds from Vindi, but not Vindi from the gaurds.  Routine for me on pull in Arena is bard circles V and his boys in a circle...I tash a gaurd out of the group to lead back for disposal...rinse, repeat, and you then have a solo Vindi...sometimes it helps to have a single fast cast spell with the outrageous aggro of Tash.
<br />

<br />
Another possibility (which happens when you rush things in the above situation) is to use your DC pets to off-tank/kill the gaurds while the MT/CH team goes to work on Vindi...you toss your baby into the fray as you kill off the extras.
<br />

<br />
Oh, and if you haven't been back that far, yet, you will need to be careful if pulling the Statue...the stairs are too tall to run back up, though you can Lull the extras hanging out with it (though they are hard to target).
<br />

<br />
