                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">a) Vindi and his guards are directly linked much in the same way a chanter and his pet is? Thus, even pacifying his guards will cause them to agro if vindi is agroed?</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
