<br />
That's the answer.  You can split the guards from Vindi by getting the guards far enough away from Vindi that he won't come to their aid.  But they are linked, and that's why any pets that are engage the guards need to a /pet back off afterwards or else they'll engage him on incoming.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
