                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">A strat that my guild uses is to have 2 pullers, either monk or sk, the first one FD's in the middle of the left arena and then the other goes and engages vindi and his 2 guards and pulls them to the middle of the arena and FD's.
<br />

<br />
Its at this point where vindi and his guards will make a b-line back to their spawn point.  If you pull him to the right location, they will walk into the corner along the edge of the arena and then vindi will warp back to spawn leaving his two guards there.  The first puller then stands to get aggro and runs them back to camp.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=450192" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.shadesofthevoid.com/images/sig/ed.jpg" border="0" /></a>
