                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I split Vindi and guards several months ago. It was likely a fluke success but here is what I did:
<br />

<br />
1. Pacified all potential adds including Guards.
<br />
2. DC a pet (im sure CoD would work fine as well)\
<br />
3. pulled vindi with boggle (guards added)
<br />
4. Ran like a sissy into the midle of the arena
<br />
5. Regained composure
<br />
6. Kited Vindi plus Guards around Ice wall had pet attack a Guard.
<br />
7. Tashed Vindi
<br />
8. At this point Vindi left the pet and attacked me.
<br />
9. AE memblur on pet and 2 Guards
<br />
10. Pulled Vindi to Raid Solo.
<br />

<br />
I was 1 rounded at that point which I am sure prevented any residual aggy on Guards from aggying the Raid. 
<br />

<br />
But I can brag I split Vindi <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="icon_wink.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
Ealdain Tinuviel
<br />
TP</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
